.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
The \fBEC\fR keytype and its parameters are described in \fBEVP_PKEY\-EC\fR\|(7).
See \fBEVP_PKEY_encapsulate\fR\|(3) and \fBEVP_PKEY_decapsulate\fR\|(3) for more info.
